# SOURCE_PAIRS_ON_SLIT_NO_FLAT -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

SOURCE_PAIRS_ON_SLIT_NO_FLAT

=head1 AUTHORS

Frossie Economou <frossie@jach.hawaii.edu>
Paul Hirst <p.hirst@jach.hawaii.edu>

=head1 DESCIPTION

The same as SOURCE_PAIRS_ON_SLIT, except that it doesn't attempt to do
flat field division, and thus works if you have (yet) not taken and
reduced flat fields.

=cut

